stnProxyTunnel.name: stnProxyTunnel
stnProxyTunnel.contactinfo: Spring Tide Networks, Inc. Customer Service Postal: 3 Clock Tower Place Suite 200 Maynard, MA 01754 USA Tel: +1 978 298 2000 Email: custserv@springtidenet.com
stnProxyTunnel.description: This MIB module describes managed objects of Spring Tide Networks Proxy Tunnel.

stnProxyTunnelTable.name: stnProxyTunnelTable
stnProxyTunnelTable.description: A list of Proxy Tunnel entries.

stnProxyTunnelEntry.name: stnProxyTunnelEntry
stnProxyTunnelEntry.description: Entry contains information about a particular Proxy Tunnel.

stnProxyTunnelSerialNumber.name: stnProxyTunnelSerialNumber
stnProxyTunnelSerialNumber.description: The serial number of the Proxy Tunnel Interface.

stnProxyTunnelRouterInstance.name: stnProxyTunnelRouterInstance
stnProxyTunnelRouterInstance.description: The instance of the router corresponding to this proxy tunnel.

stnProxyTunnelConnIdleTimeOut.name: stnProxyTunnelConnIdleTimeOut
stnProxyTunnelConnIdleTimeOut.description: The timeout in seconds that the tunnel will stay connected even if no activity takes place.

stnProxyTunnelPolicyInstance.name: stnProxyTunnelPolicyInstance
stnProxyTunnelPolicyInstance.description: The instance of the policy from which the proxy tunnel was created.

stnProxyTunnelPolicyName.name: stnProxyTunnelPolicyName
stnProxyTunnelPolicyName.description: The name of the policy associated with this proxy tunnel interface.

stnProxyTunnelEncapsType.name: stnProxyTunnelEncapsType
stnProxyTunnelEncapsType.description: The type of encapsulation used on the proxy tunnel. A value of stnProxyTunEncapsIpIp indicates an IP-IP encapsulation on the tunnel. A value of stnProxyTunEncapsIpGre indicates an IP/GRE encapsulation and a value of stnProxyTunEncapsIpsec indicates IPSEC encapsulation on the tunnel.

stnProxyTunnelState.name: stnProxyTunnelState
stnProxyTunnelState.description: The state of the proxy tunnel. A value of up indicates that the proxy tunnel is ready to send and receive data.

stnProxyTunnelL3IfaceTx.name: stnProxyTunnelL3IfaceTx
stnProxyTunnelL3IfaceTx.description: Interface index of the L3 interface over which the proxy tunnel is established. The interface corresponding to this index is used by the proxy i tunnel to send out packets.

stnProxyTunnelLocalTunnelAddr.name: stnProxyTunnelLocalTunnelAddr
stnProxyTunnelLocalTunnelAddr.description: The IP address of the local tunnel end-point.

stnProxyTunnelRemoteTunnelAddr.name: stnProxyTunnelRemoteTunnelAddr
stnProxyTunnelRemoteTunnelAddr.description: The IP address of the remote tunnel end-point.

stnProxyTunnelInESPSPIs.name: stnProxyTunnelInESPSPIs
stnProxyTunnelInESPSPIs.description: Packet array of Security Protocol Indices corresponding to incoming ESP security assocations used to encapsulate traffic on the proxy tunnel when the encapsulation type is set to IPSEC.

stnProxyTunnelOutESPSPIs.name: stnProxyTunnelOutESPSPIs
stnProxyTunnelOutESPSPIs.description: Packet array of Security Protocol Indices corresponding to outgoing ESP security assocations used to encapsulate traffic on the proxy tunnel when the encapsulation type is set to IPSEC.

stnProxyTunnelInAHSPIs.name: stnProxyTunnelInAHSPIs
stnProxyTunnelInAHSPIs.description: Packet array of Security Protocol Indices corresponding to incoming AH security assocations used to encapsulate traffic on the proxy tunnel when the encapsulation type is set to IPSEC.

stnProxyTunnelOutAHSPIs.name: stnProxyTunnelOutAHSPIs
stnProxyTunnelOutAHSPIs.description: Packet array of Security Protocol Indices corresponding to outgoing AH security assocations used to encapsulate traffic on the proxy tunnel when the encapsulation type is set to IPSEC.

stnProxyTunnelEncapsIndex.name: stnProxyTunnelEncapsIndex
stnProxyTunnelEncapsIndex.description: Index of the Encapsulation entry in the stnPmEncapsTable used to encapsulate traffic on the proxy tunnel when the encapsulation type is set IP-IP or IP-GRE.

stnProxyTunnelInPkts.name: stnProxyTunnelInPkts
stnProxyTunnelInPkts.description: The total number of packets received across the proxy tunnel.

stnProxyTunnelInErrPkts.name: stnProxyTunnelInErrPkts
stnProxyTunnelInErrPkts.description: The number of packets received across the proxy tunnel that were determined to be erroneous.

stnProxyTunnelOutPkts.name: stnProxyTunnelOutPkts
stnProxyTunnelOutPkts.description: The total number of packets sent out the proxy tunnel.

stnProxyTunnelOutErrPkts.name: stnProxyTunnelOutErrPkts
stnProxyTunnelOutErrPkts.description: The number of packets determined to be in error and discarded before sending over the tunnel.
